3222f612-7635-439a-bb59-694e7be6f9ad.do_description: To make the output, you have to...find the center of each square and add a magenta pixel to its center.  From that magenta pixel draw a line from each side of it (up, down, left, right) going straight to the border of the entire grid.  Each magenta line must reach the border of the square.  The magenta lines are allowed to cross over each other.
3222f612-7635-439a-bb59-694e7be6f9ad.grid_description: The output grid size...the same as the input.
3222f612-7635-439a-bb59-694e7be6f9ad.see_description: In the input, you should see...a light blue grid with blue square borders.

65b8f1a1-ad42-44c8-a59d-3ca17bcd96d6.do_description: To make the output, you have to... Copy the grid. color each of the centers of the outlined squares pink. Continue creating a pink line vertically up and down from this pink center cell. DO NOT color the dark Blue outline. Create a pink horizontal line left and right from the pink center cell. DO NOT color the dark Blue outline. Do this for all outlined squares. you should be done.
65b8f1a1-ad42-44c8-a59d-3ca17bcd96d6.grid_description: The output grid size...stay the same
65b8f1a1-ad42-44c8-a59d-3ca17bcd96d6.see_description: In the input, you should see... one or more 4x4 outline of squares.

736a9ad5-cb02-41ef-be0f-505d1843e7c8.do_description: To make the output, you have to...locate the center of each darker blue shape. Draw a horizontal and a vertical line in magenta, through the exact center of each shape.
736a9ad5-cb02-41ef-be0f-505d1843e7c8.grid_description: The output grid size...stays the same
736a9ad5-cb02-41ef-be0f-505d1843e7c8.see_description: In the input, you should see...a 15x15 light blue grid, containing one or more darker blue shapes.

aea9f40c-b909-4639-8ff2-b6fb8fbefb4d.do_description: To make the output, you have to...find the center of each square and add a magenta pixel to its center. From that magenta pixel draw a line from each side of it (up, down, left, right) going straight to the border of the entire grid. Each magenta line must reach the border of the grid but the lines may NOT override the blue border of the square. The magenta lines are allowed to cross over each other.
aea9f40c-b909-4639-8ff2-b6fb8fbefb4d.grid_description: The output grid size...the same as the input.
aea9f40c-b909-4639-8ff2-b6fb8fbefb4d.see_description: In the input, you should see...a light blue grid with blue square borders.
